
Tested:
	- Raspberry Pi 2
OS:
	- RASPBIAN JESSIE LITE 
Firmware:
	- Latest sudo rpi-update (20150309)
		- 8263022d59f18596ee7f4779affe620311e56862

Package(apt-get)
	- python-pygame (pyvonna)
	- flac
